    $( A condition implying that a Hilbert space operator is identically zero.
       Lemma 3.2(S8) of [Beran] p. 95. $)
    ho01i $p |- ( A. x e. ~H A. y e. ~H ( ( T ` x ) .ih y ) = 0 <->
               T = 0hop ) $=
